 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">丹泽尔·库里 (Denzel Curry)</a>在他的最新专辑《King Of The Mischievous South Vol》之前发行了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asap-rocky">A$AP Rocky</a>合作的新单曲《HOODLUMZ》。 2&#39;，于今天（7 月 19 日）发布。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/denzel-curry-cover-interview-2022-melt-my-eyez-see-your-future-3268998">丹泽尔·库里：“当今最伟大的说唱歌手？谁能告诉我我不是？”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《HOODLUMZ》是 Denzel Curry 和 A$AP Rocky 的首次合作。说唱歌手 PlayThatBoiZay 也在这首歌曲中亮相，三人在沉重而骨感的南方嘻哈节奏中吐出歌词。 A$AP Rocky 在他的歌曲中引用了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti 的</a>歌曲“RIP”，并向 1998 年的“blonde lace” <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">Eminem</a>致敬。</p><p> 《HOODLUMZ》是《King Of The Mischievous South Vol》的结束曲，是专辑尾曲的第二首。 2&#39;，库里在 2012 年突破性的混音带“King Of The Mischievous South Volume One Underground Tape 1996”的后续作品。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Denzel Curry - HOODLUMZ ft. PlayThatBoiZay 和 A$AP Rocky（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZSHSG4rP6q0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>这张专辑中，库里从 20 世纪 90 年代的南方嘻哈音乐中汲取了大量的风格灵感，这一场景诞生了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/three-6-mafia">Three 6 Mafia</a> 、DJ Screw、The Geto Boys、Kingpin Skinny Pimp 和 Tommy Wright III 等艺术家。</p><p>在《恶作剧南方之王》卷中。在《2》中，他以这种精神为基础，邀请了来自不同世代的客座艺术家，如 Three 6 Mafia 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/juicy-j">Juicy J</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/project-pat">Project Pat</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/2-chainz">2 Chainz</a> ，以及同时代的艺术家，如 Rocky、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asap-ferg">A$AP Ferg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-sign">Ty Dolla $ign</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maxo-kream">Maxo Kream</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ski-mask-the-slump-god">滑雪面具塌陷之神</a>。 Kingpin Skinny Pimp 还为专辑的前奏、结尾和间奏曲目做出了贡献。</p><p>上周日（7 月 14 日），库里与 PlayThatBoiZay 一起出现在 BBC Radio 1 的 Rap Show 中，进行了即兴表演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="丹泽尔·库里 &amp; PlayThatBoiZay|肯尼·阿尔斯塔 (Kenny Allstar) 与 Radio 1 的说唱节目独家合作" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9aUsPWD5LMw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>库里计划在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">2024 年雷丁和利兹</a>演出，该演出将于今年八月银行假日周末回归。两个地点的门票现已发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Freading-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F12885">在此处（雷丁）</a>和<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fleeds-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F35438">此处（利兹）</a>购买。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/denzel-curry-hoodlumz-asap-rocky-3776235">聆听 Denzel Curry 与 A$AP Rocky 合作的疯狂新单曲“HOODLUMZ”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
聆听 Little Simz 与 Sampha 联手深情的“卫星商业 2.0” https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business-2-0-3776230?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business- 2-0Daniel Peters Fri, 19 Jul 2024 04:20:15 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicRapUK rap https://www.nme.com/?p=3776230 <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="桑帕·利特尔·西姆兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> “一段时间以来，Simz 的音乐一直贴近我的心和耳朵”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-sampha-soulful-satellite-business-2-0-3776230">《聆听 Little Simz 与 Sampha 联手打造深情的“卫星商业 2.0”》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1392" height="884" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="桑帕·利特尔·西姆兹" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Sampha-LittleSimz-Getty-AFord-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sampha">Sampha</a>发行了“Satellite Business 2.0”，这是他的“Lahai”曲目的扩展版本，现在由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a>主演。听下面的曲目。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/little-simz-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-stage-setlist-photos-3770489">Little Simz 在 Glastonbury 2024：一位历史上伟大的英国说唱歌手登上了头条新闻的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首新单曲是 Sampha 2023 年第二张专辑中插曲《Satellite Business》的扩展。 “《Satellite Business》是《Lahai》最后录制的曲目之一，我一直想用一首客串诗来扩展它，”他在<a href="https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/sampha-and-little-simz-link-up-on-satellite-business-2-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《The Line of Best Fit》</em></a>的一份新闻声明中说道。</p><p> “一段时间以来，Simz 的音乐一直贴近我的心和耳朵，这让她在这首歌中的表现更加特别。她是我最喜欢的艺术家之一。她的自信和创造性的勇气令人耳目一新，看到有人为自己的艺术付出如此多的努力真是令人惊奇”。</p><p>与此同时，Little Simz 表示，她“非常荣幸能与 Sampha 一起制作这张唱片”，并称他“确实是当今音乐界最重要的声音之一”。她补充道：“我们有很好的音乐化学反应，并且尊重彼此的过程。很高兴我能在这件事上与他站在一起。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sampha 和 Little Simz - 卫星业务 2.0" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/THre1r5KGR0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Sampha 在 Instagram 帖子中详细阐述了“Satellite Business 2.0”的起源，称这首原创歌曲“是在去年的现场演奏中演变而来的”，观众的反响激励他继续创作这首新歌曲。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C9fhlfLNK1r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; 